blogs.title: If I try to fail, but I succeed, which one did I actually do?
blogs.body:
Have I failed at failing? Or have I succeeded despite my attempts to fail? What is success, and what is failure?

Why is success sometimes more terrifying than failure? When is failure better for you than success?
blogs.author: Johnny B. Good

blogs.title: If con is the opposite of pro, is congress the opposite of progress?
blogs.body: So, is it possible to have progress in congress? Or is that an oxymoron? And what is it about congress, specifically, that impedes progress? And has that been its purpose all along?
blogs.author: J. Caesar
